text.section:
The certificate required under subsection (a) of this section shall be signed by one of the following:
a medical doctor who is authorized to practice medicine or surgery by the state in which the doctor practices;
if authorized to practice in a state and performing within the scope of that authority:
a chiropractor;
a clinical psychologist;
a dentist;
a licensed certified social worker - clinical;
a nurse midwife;
a nurse practitioner;
an oral surgeon;
an optometrist;
a physical therapist; or
a podiatrist;
an accredited Christian Science practitioner; or
a health care provider as defined by the federal Family Medical Leave Act.
